**Medium Risk:**
- Masonry layout edge cases (overlapping widgets)
- Responsive behavior (3x → 2x → 1x transitions)
- Testing all widget combinations

**Mitigation:**
- Test thoroughly with different widget combinations
- Use browser DevTools responsive mode
- Add smooth transitions to prevent jarring layout shifts
- Set max-width constraints if needed

